{{distinguish|维权律师}}

'''人权律师'''狭义指從事人权法（包括国际法及国內法）的專業人权捍卫者，以保障人免受如酷刑和其他形式虐待<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/zh/events/humanrightsday/2010/profiles.shtml|title=2010年人权日，大声疾呼，制止歧视！|website=联合国|accessdate=2018-12-04|archive-date=2019-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923124715/https://www.un.org/zh/events/humanrightsday/2010/profiles.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iolaw.org.cn/showArticle.asp?id=2534|title=互联网上的国际人权法资源研究|website=中国法学网|accessdate=2018-12-04|archive-date=2019-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720222714/http://www.iolaw.org.cn/showArticle.asp?id=2534|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://unp.un.org/details.aspx?entry=C09044 |title=Handbook on Criminal Justice Responses to Terrorism (中文) |accessdate=2013-10-04 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004225634/https://unp.un.org/details.aspx?entry=C09044 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://education-portal.com/articles/Human_Rights_Lawyer_Job_Information_and_Requirements_for_Becoming_a_Human_Rights_Attorney.html|title=Human Rights Lawyer: Job Info & Requirements|publisher=|accessdate=2018-12-04|archive-date=2015-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225005158/http://education-portal.com/articles/Human_Rights_Lawyer_Job_Information_and_Requirements_for_Becoming_a_Human_Rights_Attorney.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為眾多人权捍卫者專業司法及執法人員種類中的一項<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.un.org/chinese/hr/issue/justice.htm|title=联合国人权事务|website=联合国|accessdate=2018-12-04|archive-date=2020-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402104500/https://www.un.org/chinese/hr/issue/justice.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦有广义观点指出，因为律师基本原则是要保护人权<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.umn.edu/humanrts/chinese/CHi3bprl.htm|title=University of Minnesota Chinese Page|website=University of Minnesota Twin Cities|accessdate=2018-12-04|archive-date=2013-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005000908/http://www1.umn.edu/humanrts/chinese/CHi3bprl.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，所以「法治国家的律师全是人权律师」<ref>[http://www.szlib.gov.cn/Search/searchdetail.jsp?v_tablearray=bibliosm&v_recno=644350&v_curtable=bibliosm&site= 维权律师，一个危险的职业/ 刘路著]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

